Seahorse build environment
==========================

0. Overview

    Scripts for building all Seahorse docker images from source.
    In order to avoid problems with build dependencies, the build process is performed inside
    a Docker container.
    The script will clone required repositories from GitHub, build all projects, create Dockerfiles
    and build docker images.

1. Requirements

    1.1 docker (https://docs.docker.com/engine/installation/)
    1.2 git access to Codilime repos:
        - https://github.com/codilime/deepsense-backend-tap.git
        - https://github.com/codilime/deepsense-frontend-tap.git

2. Usage

    2.1 To build the dockers execute:
        $ ./run.sh

3. Files

    3.1 README
        This file.
    3.2 run.sh
        Main script building all components.
    3.3 Dockerfile
        Build env docker image.
    3.4 build.sh
        Script for building the components inside the docker container.

